Paper: hep-th/9404075

Date: 1994-04-13

Title: On Marshak's and Connes' views of chirality

Authors: J. M. Gracia-Bondia

Comments: 10 pages, Plain TeX

I render the substance of the discussions I had with Robert E. Marshakshortly before his death, wherein the kinship between the ``neutrino paradigm''geometry (NCG) was found. In that context, we give a brief account of theConnes--Lott reconstruction of the Standard Model (SM).